title: Digital Tutors - Creating a Medical Illustration in CINEMA 4D -
description:
1h 38m

Difficulty Level Advanced

 Project Files Included 

Software used
CINEMA 4D 14 and Photoshop CS6

What you will learn
In this CINEMA 4D tutorial we will learn how to create a 3D medical illustration. Throughout these lessons we will look at the steps and techniques, including modeling, texturing and more used to create this stylized medical illustration using CINEMA 4D and Photoshop.

Guest Tutor

Andy Lefton
from the Creative Development series

10 Lessons
